reviewText: SUPER SHOW!  Fun for kids and adults alike!  Shows many Alaskan animals (polar bear, Bald Eagles, Moose and more) plus activities that the Alaskans participate in.  Includes video and information about the Fur Rondy, the Iditarod and shows some of Martin Buser's kennel and his dogs.  Also has some clips of Susan Butcher on the Iditarod Trail.  EXCELLENT!
